{"data":[{"name":"99:1","price":"大地が激しく震動させられる時、","arabic":"إِذَا زُلۡزِلَتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ زِلۡزَالَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6139,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā zul'zilati al-arḍu zil'zālahā ","translations":["When","is shaken","the earth","(with) its earthquake","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","zul'zilati","al-arḍu","zil'zālahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1730],[3,1730,2580],[4,2580,4295]]}},{"name":"99:2","price":"また、大地がその重荷¹を吐き出し、","arabic":"وَأَخۡرَجَتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ أَثۡقَالَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6140,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「重荷」は、死んだ人々や、財宝のこととされる（ムヤッサル５９９頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akhrajati al-arḍu athqālahā ","translations":["And brings forth","the earth","its burdens","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akhrajati","al-arḍu","athqālahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1380],[2,1380,2170],[3,2170,3865]]}},{"name":"99:3","price":"（戦慄に襲われた）人間が「それ（大地）に、何が起こったのか？」と言う時、¹","arabic":"وَقَالَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا لَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6141,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　復活の日の天変地異の様子については、洞窟章４７、ター・ハー章１０５－１０７、蟻章８８、山章９－１０、出来事章５ー６、衣を纏（まと）う 者章１４、真実章１３－１５、階段章８－９、消息章２０、巻き込む章３、衝撃章４－５なども参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waqāla al-insānu mā lahā ","translations":["And says","man","What","(is) with it","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["waqāla","al-insānu","mā","lahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,3310],[3,3310,3790],[4,3790,4495]]}},{"name":"99:4","price":"それ（（大地）は（復活の）その日、自らの消息¹を話す、","arabic":"يَوۡمَئِذٖ تُحَدِّثُ أَخۡبَارَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6142,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「消息」とは、大地で行われた善悪の行いのこと（ムヤッサル５９９頁参照）。 あるいは大地の変動の理由（アル＝バイダーウィー５：５１８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma-idhin tuḥaddithu akhbārahā ","translations":["That Day","it will report","its news","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma-idhin","tuḥaddithu","akhbārahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2180],[2,2180,3220],[3,3220,4875]]}},{"name":"99:5","price":"あなたの主*が、（そうするよう、）自分にご命じになったのだ、ということを。¹","arabic":"بِأَنَّ رَبَّكَ أَوۡحَىٰ لَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6143,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「・・・自分にお伝えになったために」という解釈もある（前掲書、同頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-anna rabbaka awḥā lahā ","translations":["Because","your Lord","inspired","[to] it","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-anna","rabbaka","awḥā","lahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1750],[2,1750,2690],[3,2690,3560],[4,3560,4215]]}},{"name":"99:6","price":"その日、人々は自分たちの行いを見るべく、三々五々に出て行く¹。","arabic":"يَوۡمَئِذٖ يَصۡدُرُ ٱلنَّاسُ أَشۡتَاتٗا لِّيُرَوۡاْ أَعۡمَٰلَهُمۡ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6144,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　清算の場から、天国、または地獄へと連れて行かれる。あるいは、墓場から清算の場へと出て行く（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：１４９－１５０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma-idhin yaṣduru al-nāsu ashtātan liyuraw aʿmālahum ","translations":["That Day","will proceed","the mankind","(in) scattered groups","to be shown","their deeds","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma-idhin","yaṣduru","al-nāsu","ashtātan","liyuraw","aʿmālahum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2010],[2,2010,2830],[3,2830,4460],[4,4460,5540],[5,5540,6560],[6,6560,8515]]}},{"name":"99:7","price":"それで、僅かな重みでも善いことを行う者は誰でも、（来世で）それ（に対する褒美）を見出すのであり、","arabic":"فَمَن يَعۡمَلۡ مِثۡقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ خَيۡرٗا يَرَهُۥ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6145,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"faman yaʿmal mith'qāla dharratin khayran yarahu ","translations":["So whoever","does","(equal to the) weight","(of) an atom","good","will see it","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["faman","yaʿmal","mith'qāla","dharratin","khayran","yarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,4250],[5,4250,5050],[6,5050,7025]]}},{"name":"99:8","price":"僅かな重みでも悪いことを行う者は誰でも、（来世で）それ（に対する応報）を見出すのだ。¹","arabic":"وَمَن يَعۡمَلۡ مِثۡقَالَ ذَرَّةٖ شَرّٗا يَرَهُۥ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6146,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　同様の意味のアーヤ*として、婦人章４０、洞窟章４９、預言者*たち章４７、ルクマーン章１６なども参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waman yaʿmal mith'qāla dharratin sharran yarahu ","translations":["And whoever","does","(equal to the) weight","(of) an atom","evil","will see it","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["waman","yaʿmal","mith'qāla","dharratin","sharran","yarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,550],[2,550,2460],[3,2460,3640],[4,3640,4820],[5,4820,6790],[6,6790,9315]]}}],"chapter":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah","Chapter Az-Zalzalah","Zalzalah","Surah Zalzalah","Chapter Zalzalah","Az Zalzalah","Surah Az Zalzalah","Chapter Az Zalzalah","Surah 99","Chapter 99","The Earthquake","الزلزلة"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}